	Attribute for forcing serialization of enum fields by name instead of by value.
Example:

---
enum Color {
	red,
	green,
	blue
}

struct Test {
	// serialized as an int (e.g. 1 for Color.green)
	Color color;
	// serialized as a string (e.g. "green" for Color.green)
	@byName Color namedColor;
